      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELLIS STREET (3) has been very good in winning his two starts here since joining the Donny Smith stable, getting home by 4.6m last week. Came from one spot wider when too strong at this distance prior. Big chance to land the hat trick. CALL TO ORDER (1) hit his peak at the latest appearance when he led from wider and kept going to score by 2.7 metres. Can take advantage of the inside barrier. Leading hope. COOL NIGHT (2) draws well again and is a player off a last-start win by 3 metres at this venue. OZZIE PUNTA (8) has added to a string of top-four results by finishing runner-up to ELLIS STREET in his last two outings. Owns a good record at this circuit and distance so include again.",
